==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Yawl-rigged
<hw>Yawl"-rigged"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Naut.)</fld>
<def>Having two masts with fore-and-aft sails, but differing from a
schooner in that the after mast is very small, and stepped as far aft as
possible. See <xex>Illustration</xex> in Appendix.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Yawn</ent>⟦br⟧
